ai.grakn.graql

Interface Printer<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the intermediate representation that can be converted into a string

    public interface Printer<T>
    Interface describing a way to print Graql objects. For example, if you wanted something that could convert Graql into a YAML representation, you might make a YamlPrinter implements Printer<Yaml>, that would convert everything into a Yaml and define a method to convert a Yaml into a String.
    Author:
    Felix Chapman
